ALTTEX is and innovative system which consists of a decentralized crypto exchange, crypto messenger, and crypto safe. Our system allows people to buy cryptocurrencies from any place in the world with any bank card.  ALTTEX is a unique platform for mobile devices, which combines all the advanced technologies of blockchain. Crypto-exchange in Mobile App  Buy Cryptocurrency with one click, using your credit card. The exchange is designed specifically for mobile devices with Face ID and Touch ID  Messenger With Custom Store  In the crypto messenger you can not only communicate with the list of your contacts, creating groups, public channels, secret chats, but also add your goods in the application and sell them for any cryptocurrency.  Smart Secure Safe  In early 2017, the capitalization of the cryptocurrency was $11 billion, 10 months later it was already $300 billion And only small percentage of people can save all cryptocurrencies in one secure place. To do this we develop a special application Smart Safe, which will save your cryptocurrencies and will send push notifications on your device with all changes in their price and your current profit for the selected period  ROADMAP MEET THE TEAM  Our team has united the best who have huge experience of creating and developing internet source   VIDEO INTRODUCTION you can check this promotional video below!
